DATASET ATTRIBUTION & LICENSES:

1. APIBench
   - URL: https://huggingface.co/datasets/gorilla-llm/APIBench
   - License: CC BY 4.0
   - Citation: Xu et al., "API-Bank: A Comprehensive Benchmark for Tool-Augmented LLMs", 2023

2. ToolBench
   - URL: https://huggingface.co/datasets/tuandunghcmut/toolbench-v1
   - License: Apache 2.0
   - Citation: Qin et al., "ToolBench: A Benchmark for Language Models on Tool Use", 2023

3. Gorilla BFCL (Berkeley Function-Calling Leaderboard)
   - URL: https://huggingface.co/datasets/gorilla-llm/Berkeley-Function-Calling-Leaderboard
   - License: MIT
   - Citation: Patil et al., "Gorilla: Large Language Model Connected to Large Tools", 2023

4. Synthetic Data
   - Generated via scripts/generate_synthetic.py (template-based)
   - License: CC BY 4.0
   - Source: Custom generation with deterministic seed

